<topic id="rng-hierarchy-view">
  <title>RNG Resource Hierarchy/Dependencies View</title>
  <prolog>
    <metadata>
      <keywords><indexterm>Relax NG schemas<indexterm>Resource Hierarchy/Dependencies view</indexterm></indexterm></keywords>
    </metadata>
  </prolog>
  <body>
    <p>The <uicontrol>Resource Hierarchy/Dependencies</uicontrol> view allows you to see the
      hierarchy/dependencies for a schema. <ph conkeyref="reusables-user-guide/reopen-view"/></p>
    <p>If you want to see the hierarchy of a schema, select the desired schema in the <xref
        href="using-the-project-view.dita#using-the-project-view"><uicontrol
          product="developer editor">Project</uicontrol><uicontrol
          product="developerEclipse editorEclipse">Navigator</uicontrol> view</xref> and choose
        <uicontrol>Resource Hierarchy</uicontrol> from the contextual menu.</p>
    <p>
      <fig>
        <title>Resource Hierarchy/Dependencies View - hierarchy for
          <filepath>map.rng</filepath></title>
        <image href="../img/sa_rng_hierarchy.png" placement="inline"/>
      </fig>
    </p>
    <p>If you want to see the dependencies of a schema, select the desired schema in the <uicontrol
        product="developer editor">Project</uicontrol><uicontrol
        product="developerEclipse editorEclipse">Navigator</uicontrol> view and choose
        <uicontrol>Resource Dependencies</uicontrol> from the contextual menu.</p>
    <p>
      <fig>
        <title>Resource Hierarchy/Dependencies View - Dependencies for
            <filepath>tblDecl.mod.rng</filepath></title>
        <image href="../img/sa_rng_dependencies.png" placement="inline"/>
      </fig>
    </p>
    <p conkeyref="reusables-editing-documents/hierarchy-dependencies-toolbar-actions"/>
    <p conkeyref="reusables-editing-documents/contextual-menu"/>
    <p>
      <note>The <uicontrol>Move resource</uicontrol> or <uicontrol>Rename resource</uicontrol>
        actions give you the option to <xref
          href="move-rename-resource-wsdl-hierarchy-view.dita#move-rename-resource-wsdl-hierarchy-view"
          >update the references to the resource</xref>.</note>
    </p>
  </body>
